author: @GyulBoo
text:
Really warms the heart how they seem so much more attentive and affectionate to Seungkwan here. From Joshua making him laugh like crazy with that Love Shot dance and Jeonghan and Woozi repeating it because it made him laugh so much to Wonwoo being on his phone the entire time but turning it off when Seungkwan came to hug him (26:00), DK telling him to have a good night so sweetly after Seungkwan said goodnight (26:12), and Hoshi scooting over to hold him in a bear hug while they are lying down (26:20), they are being so affectionate to him here, knowing the tragedy he just went through ❤❤❤❤

They also tried to give him screentime with that acrostic poem at 4:12 because he was not being talkative, but still reassuring him that it was okay when he couldn't do the poem, especially considering that they would have mercilessly teased him had it been any other day or episode.
